{"type":null,"faqId":48022,"title":"联系人群组","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.15625in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>您可以将存储在手机中的联系人添加到群组，并轻松向群组发送信息或电子邮件。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>                </span><span class=\"s1\">创建联系人群组</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"创建联系人群组\"XE \"新建群组\"XE \"创建群组\"XE \"创建通讯录群组\"XE \"创建联系人群组\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177841\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“联系人”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>点击“我的群组”，然后点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177842\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>输入群组名称，然后点击“确定”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">4.  </span><span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177843\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">5.  </span><span>选择要添加到群组的联系人，或点击“全选”选择所有联系人，然后点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177844\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">编辑联系人群组</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"编辑联系人群组\"XE \"修改联系人群组\"XE \"编辑通讯录群组\"XE \"修改通讯录群组\"XE \"将联系人分组\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177845\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“联系人”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.点击“我的群组”，然后选择要编辑的群组。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177846\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”添加新成员。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177847\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，选择以下一种操作：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>点击“移除成员”删除群组中的成员。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>点击“删除群组”删除该群组。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>点击“重命名”修改群组名称。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">给群组发信息或电子邮件</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"给群组发信息或电子邮件\"XE \"给群组发信息\"XE \"给群组发电子邮件\"XE \"群发信息\"XE \"群发电子邮件\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177848\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“联系人”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.点击“我的群组”，选择要发送信息或邮件的群组。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177849\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”发送信息，或点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177850\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”发送邮件。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>       </span><span class=\"s1\">         删除群组</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"删除群组\"XE \"解散群组\"XE \"取消联系人分组\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177851\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“联系人”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.点击“我的群组”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.长按要删除的群组，然后点击“删除”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.点击“删除”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177852\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>删除群组不会删除群组中的联系人。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3608","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598092000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":58,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}